      "id": "PopularPost60033",
      "post_content": "Fear is a nice evasion ability, and a creature with fear can really wreak havoc on non-black decks. However, like [Terror](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Terror), Fear is completely useless against other black decks and decks that use a lot of artifact creatures. The casting cost of this particular aura makes it unsplashable, so users are going to be playing primarily black decks. Fear is a great addition to any creature, but particularly good on any creature you want to get through for damage like [Hypnotic Specter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hypnotic Specter) or fragile creatures with decent abilities like [El-Hajjaj](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=El-Hajjaj).",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost60033\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">Fear is a nice evasion ability, and a creature with fear can really wreak havoc on non-black decks.  However, like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Terror\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Terror\">Terror</a>, Fear is completely useless against other black decks and decks that use a lot of artifact creatures.  The casting cost of this particular aura makes it unsplashable, so users are going to be playing primarily black decks.  Fear is a great addition to any creature, but particularly good on any creature you want to get through for damage like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hypnotic Specter\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hypnotic Specter\">Hypnotic Specter</a> or fragile creatures with decent abilities like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"El-Hajjaj\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=El-Hajjaj\">El-Hajjaj</a>.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '60033'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy525\">Eppek_the_Goblin</span>\r\n                                (3/14/2010 8:20:38 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n          